{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658700/extras/Discord_Banner_for_Steam.gif?t=1727985689\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the Stellar Nexus, the strongest fighters of the multiverse clash in an epic battle to determine who will be the best SNIPERPUNK. Cyberpunk, Decopunk, Raypunk, and Steampunk will duke it out in order to prove themselves worthy and become champions of the Stellar Nexus. Each punk comes equipped with different abilities and their own unique punk-style weapon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658700/extras/entrance_anims.gif?t=1727985689\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>PLAY ONLINE OR LOCALLY</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle in 1v1 First To 7 (Win by 2) Matches</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Test your skill with Online Matchmaking</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play in Private Lobbies</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create Custom Matches</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658700/extras/Zone.gif?t=1727985689\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>POWERUP YOUR PUNK</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose items between rounds to power up your punk further. The longer you play, the more havoc you can create for your opponent. Pick items that increase stats. Some items even allow for added effects to your attacks, like allowing all bullets to explode!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658700/extras/gifitemselect.gif?t=1727985689\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>BULLET HELL ACTION</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this action-packed bullet hell, you aim to create combinations that pressure your opponent and prevent them from evading damage. Each punk has a unique ability and a special dodge to help them achieve that goal. Stay cautious because it\u2019s easy to damage yourself in the crossfire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658700/extras/bullet_hell.gif?t=1727985689\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>45 UNIQUE MAPS TO CHOOSE FROM</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On top of the basic map theme, each punk character comes with a unique theme and arena mechanic. You can choose from 9 different arena layouts for each theme, creating 45 map combinations and limitless replayability. All themes and layouts are available from the start so explore to your heart's content!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658700/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727985689","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658700/page.bg.jpg?t=1727985689","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658700/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727985689","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1658700/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727985689","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=